{"tid":1732211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我好撚辛苦呀","createTime":"2019-11-18T00:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T00:38:05.000Z","uid":41366,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f80864a8a0e574e7b27994089912b1e6db0dea","tid":1732211,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:17:34.000Z","msg":"屌無老母琴晚發夢俾班狗推進<br />\n由佐敦推撚到旺角東<br />\n我唔敢講前線手足冇做野<br />\n因為班狗開撚左實彈果下<br />\n我地完全失晒方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每一下都後退，後退<br />\n每次都好夠人手去防<br />\n老實講我地開始冇左一個正常攻勢<br />\n都好合理既，因為武力唔對等<br />\n我地出面同理大手足一樣好徬徨無助<br />\n推到旺角東果下，我地成班手足散左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到朝早變晒裝行到尖沙咀，班賤狗完全包抄<br />\n冇撚人性，想逼死我地手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我求下你地，可唔可以幫幫手呀<br />\n唔開花，都塞下鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三罷呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻要靠聞到tg先敢爆喊呀，屌你老母<br />\n我好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我唔知可以做咩<br />\n只可以出個post發洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbde6fd08d07331e42c84072a808eeb145152f4","tid":1732211,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:19:45.000Z","msg":"出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4d9b345bc40a3dd1c9e8390271904d16ce050d","tid":1732211,"uid":27362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:20:12.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8b9184f14ca791c1bbed1250088b0385784832","tid":1732211,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:20:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c1d850cacf81d82b11de9884a5bd3b5d143fe78c","tid":1732211,"uid":41366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:21:56.000Z","msg":"我唔會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都唔想poly手足俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想再犧牲手足，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d51430baaa3d001ef57435718a2e695097320c4","tid":1732211,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:24:33.000Z","msg":"成班返工，幾時仆街死<br />\n你地適應力係咁撚強呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0ca8417f4491585360ccbb138dbb59bff0b3f3","tid":1732211,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:25:12.000Z","msg":"我呢一刻我唔知點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji